## TPickPartial type

Like `Partial` but allows specification of optional properties.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type TPickPartial<T, K extends keyof T> = Pick<T, Exclude<keyof T, K>> & Partial<Pick<T, K>>;
```
